435
00:47:27,539 --> 00:47:30,840
[SPEAKER_02] Imala je visoku proizvodnju želje za svega.

436
00:47:30,840 --> 00:47:32,420
[SPEAKER_02] Onda su se dogodile

437
00:47:32,420 --> 00:47:34,059
[SPEAKER_02] te velike promjene

438
00:47:34,059 --> 00:47:36,079
[SPEAKER_02] kad je zapad

439
