469
00:48:52,519 --> 00:48:53,639
[SPEAKER_02] Da, Trumpovih carina,

470
00:48:53,639 --> 00:48:56,860
[SPEAKER_02] i to je jedan veliki pritisak na njezinu ekonomiju.

471
00:48:56,860 --> 00:49:02,739
