[SPEAKER_02] da je vodej elita.

477
00:49:15,519 --> 00:49:17,219
[SPEAKER_02] I to je vrlo bitno,

478
00:49:17,219 --> 00:49:19,239
[SPEAKER_02] da je vode najpametniji ljudi,

479
00:49:19,239 --> 00:49:21,219
