487
00:49:37,400 --> 00:49:42,039
[SPEAKER_02] voditi takve velike provincije i gradove.

488
00:49:42,039 --> 00:49:45,400
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo, ona ima taj plan koliko se got nama činilo

489
