[SPEAKER_02] da je to zastarijalo.

490
00:49:46,440 --> 00:49:48,239
[SPEAKER_02] To su oni preuzeli od Rusa,

491
00:49:48,239 --> 00:49:49,579
[SPEAKER_02] te petoljetke,

492
00:49:49,579 --> 00:49:52,159
[SPEAKER_02] mislim da od 53. godine već.

493
00:49:52,159 --> 00:49:55,500
[SPEAKER_02] Ali oni te planove rade vrlo ozbjeno.

494
00:49:55,500 --> 00:49:56,659
[SPEAKER_02] Sad je, recimo,

495
00:49:56,659 --> 00:49:59,019
[SPEAKER_02] partija dala smjernice.

496
00:49:59,019 --> 00:50:02,219
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, da se ide dalje u tehnološki razvoj,

497
00:50:02,219 --> 00:50:04,420
[SPEAKER_02] kako će se voditi vanjska politika,

498
00:50:04,420 --> 00:50:08,760
[SPEAKER_02] kako da se privuku ulaganja strana,

499
00:50:08,760 --> 00:50:11,199
[SPEAKER_02] kako da se poveća zaposlenost.

500
00:50:11,199 --> 00:50:14,039
[SPEAKER_02] Je veliki problem sa zaposlenost u mladi.

501
00:50:14,639 --> 00:50:16,820
[SPEAKER_02] I to će se dalje razrađivati.

502
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:17,760
[SPEAKER_02] Postoji jedna

503
00:50:17,760 --> 00:50:20,519
[SPEAKER_02] reformska razvojna komisija Kine.

504
00:50:20,519 --> 00:50:22,199
[SPEAKER_02] To je vrlo važno tijelo,

505
00:50:22,199 --> 00:50:24,599
[SPEAKER_02] koje će onda sad sve te predloge

506
00:50:24,599 --> 00:50:25,960
[SPEAKER_02] razraditi.

507
00:50:25,960 --> 00:50:26,380
[SPEAKER_02] A znači,

508
00:50:26,380 --> 00:50:29,280
[SPEAKER_02] vi vidite tu jednu političku podršku za razvoj.

509
00:50:29,280 --> 00:50:30,659
[SPEAKER_02] To je jako bitno.

510
00:50:30,659 --> 00:50:32,940
[SPEAKER_02] Jer za svaku državu je najvažnije

511
00:50:32,940 --> 00:50:34,139
[SPEAKER_02] da ima dobrovodstvo.

512
00:50:34,519 --> 00:50:37,420
[SPEAKER_02] Da, oni imaju to dobrovodstvo drugo.

513
00:50:37,420 --> 00:50:40,780
[SPEAKER_02] Kina se isto bori stalno protiv korupcije.

514
00:50:40,780 --> 00:50:42,739
[SPEAKER_02] Nekoliko ljudi, osam generala,

515
00:50:42,739 --> 00:50:44,260
[SPEAKER_02] ne znam koliko je sad smijenjeno,

516
00:50:44,260 --> 00:50:49,760
[SPEAKER_02] koji su bili u tom centralnom komitetu.

517
00:50:49,760 --> 00:50:55,699
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, Kina je sve to što je napravila

518
00:50:55,699 --> 00:50:56,820
[SPEAKER_02] u prošlogodničnom pravju maljne,

519
00:50:56,820 --> 00:50:58,139
[SPEAKER_02] više ona je postigla.

520
00:50:58,139 --> 00:51:01,039
[SPEAKER_02] Pogledajte njezin izvoz,

521
00:51:01,039 --> 00:51:02,400
[SPEAKER_02] koji su to proizvodi,

522
00:51:02,400 --> 00:51:04,139
